1
00:00:11,710 --> 00:00:14,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I should rest while I can.</font>

2
00:00:16,330 --> 00:00:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hiya!</font>

3
00:00:18,380 --> 00:00:19,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The kidnapper!</font>

4
00:00:21,460 --> 00:00:22,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can't move.</font>

5
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can't speak, either!</font>

6
00:00:26,540 --> 00:00:29,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's no use! I immobilized you.</font>

7
00:00:29,750 --> 00:00:32,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Beautifully divine handiwork!</font>

8
00:00:32,250 --> 00:00:34,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm Kuusetsu.</font>

9
00:00:34,170 --> 00:00:36,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She's one of the Eight Thunder Gods!</font>

10
00:00:36,420 --> 00:00:40,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I got back to my lair
and my lookouts were dead,</font>

11
00:00:40,040 --> 00:00:41,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and my prey had escaped!</font>

12
00:00:41,790 --> 00:00:43,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">My plan was totally foiled!</font>

13
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I wanted to lose my cool and raise hell,</font>

14
00:00:45,960 --> 00:00:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">but Big Sis Shikoku
forbade me from fighting.</font>

15
00:00:48,630 --> 00:00:51,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Then I saw you and followed you here!</font>

16
00:00:52,130 --> 00:00:53,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Me?</font>

17
00:00:53,210 --> 00:00:54,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yuuki Wakura.</font>

18
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:58,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Big Sis Shikoku's favorite.
I've heard a lot about you.</font>

19
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:03,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So I might as well bring you back
as a souvenir from Yokohama.</font>

20
00:01:03,710 --> 00:01:04,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">My body just-</font>

21
00:01:05,130 --> 00:01:07,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And I need you for my test.</font>

22
00:01:07,460 --> 00:01:10,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You'll do, I guess. Barely.</font>

23
00:01:10,210 --> 00:01:11,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">"Test"?</font>

24
00:01:12,540 --> 00:01:14,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Before I snatched one of my prey...</font>

25
00:01:15,330 --> 00:01:17,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">she was having sex with a male.</font>

26
00:01:18,250 --> 00:01:22,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I wanna know if it feels
as good as it looked.</font>

27
00:01:24,330 --> 00:01:27,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">M-my tongue... and my arms...</font>

28
00:01:27,540 --> 00:01:29,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They're moving on their own!</font>

29
00:01:31,080 --> 00:01:33,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Mm, this is nice.</font>

30
00:01:35,630 --> 00:01:39,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I wonder what happens to a human
when they have sex with a god.</font>

31
00:01:41,290 --> 00:01:43,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Should we test it out?</font>

32
00:01:44,540 --> 00:01:47,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Test it? Sex with a god?!</font>

33
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:50,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Nectar of a god.</font>

34
00:01:50,630 --> 00:01:52,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Don't waste a single drop.</font>

35
00:02:14,580 --> 00:02:17,540
<font size="21"><b>{\an7}Area exercises for circles</b></font>

36
00:02:15,330 --> 00:02:16,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, I get it!</font>

37
00:02:18,790 --> 00:02:21,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thanks for the help, Miss Himari!</font>

38
00:02:21,420 --> 00:02:24,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Just use the ratio and the formula.</font>

39
00:02:24,670 --> 00:02:26,080
<font size="46" color="#ff80c0"><b>{\an7}Yokohama</b></font>

40
00:02:24,670 --> 00:02:26,080
<font size="46" color="#91c8ff"><b>{\an7}Travel</b></font>

41
00:02:24,670 --> 00:02:26,080
<font size="40" color="#ff8080"><b>{\an7}Chinatown</b></font>

42
00:02:26,130 --> 00:02:28,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I wish I could go to Yokohama.</font>

43
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The commanders are there on a mission.</font>

44
00:02:33,210 --> 00:02:36,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yeah, but imagine
the city's skyline at night!</font>

45
00:02:36,420 --> 00:02:39,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Just the thought is so romantic!</font>

46
00:02:46,670 --> 00:02:47,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's beautiful.</font>

47
00:02:51,170 --> 00:02:53,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're even more beautiful, Shushu.</font>

48
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:54,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh?!</font>

49
00:02:55,500 --> 00:02:59,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There's something
different about you, Yukki.</font>

50
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:10,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can't hold back any longer.</font>

51
00:03:10,580 --> 00:03:11,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh?</font>

52
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:14,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You won't be getting any sleep tonight.</font>

53
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:22,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh my god, as if!</font>

54
00:03:24,830 --> 00:03:26,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Quit messing around.</font>

55
00:03:26,250 --> 00:03:28,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They're up against a Thunder God.</font>

56
00:03:28,420 --> 00:03:30,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They could be facing a situation
more dangerous</font>

57
00:03:30,710 --> 00:03:33,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">than anything we've ever imagined.</font>

58
00:03:49,580 --> 00:03:51,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Aw, look at that scowl.</font>

59
00:03:54,330 --> 00:03:56,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're just a little numb right now.</font>

60
00:03:57,040 --> 00:03:58,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's harmless.</font>

61
00:03:59,080 --> 00:04:02,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So relax and let yourself be mesmerized.</font>

62
00:04:08,580 --> 00:04:10,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This scent...</font>

63
00:04:13,580 --> 00:04:15,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This sensation...</font>

64
00:04:18,960 --> 00:04:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This taste...</font>

65
00:04:25,830 --> 00:04:27,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I like all of it.</font>

66
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now, let's make it feel even better, hm?</font>

67
00:04:33,540 --> 00:04:36,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You should be able to move a bit now.</font>

68
00:04:39,130 --> 00:04:43,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So dedicate your tongue
to every last inch of your god.</font>

69
00:04:47,750 --> 00:04:49,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">C'mon, hurry up.</font>

70
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:54,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">MISS MIRA!</font>

71
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Who are you?</font>

72
00:05:15,580 --> 00:05:20,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">My heart sunk and I no longer feel hope for the future</font>

73
00:05:20,500 --> 00:05:25,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">It felt like time froze and now it's all over</font>

74
00:05:25,670 --> 00:05:28,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Brooding and silent</font>

75
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:31,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">The umbrella of my heart began to open</font>

76
00:05:31,670 --> 00:05:35,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Still, I kept my chin up and went on</font>

77
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:39,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">I won't ask you to comfort me</font>

78
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">I want to grow strong and focus on what's ahead</font>

79
00:05:44,790 --> 00:05:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">But weakness crushes me</font>

80
00:05:52,630 --> 00:05:57,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Meeting you is what filled my world with light</font>

81
00:05:57,670 --> 00:06:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">I didn't have an ounce of hope, and yet I could laugh</font>

82
00:06:02,540 --> 00:06:07,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Ordinary conversations always brought me a smile</font>

83
00:06:07,330 --> 00:06:11,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">I won't say thanks 'cause you'll blush and laugh</font>

84
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">But I'm thinking it</font>

85
00:06:12,540 --> 00:06:16,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Can I move forward from here?</font>

86
00:06:16,580 --> 00:06:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">O light, come to me</font>

87
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:35,960
<font size="46"><b>A Commander's Resolve</b></font>

88
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:35,960
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Episode 9</b></font>

89
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This sensation...</font>

90
00:06:43,580 --> 00:06:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This taste...</font>

91
00:06:50,380 --> 00:06:52,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I like all of it.</font>

92
00:06:52,460 --> 00:06:55,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now, let's make it feel even better, hm?</font>

93
00:06:57,880 --> 00:07:00,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You should be able to move a bit now.</font>

94
00:07:03,420 --> 00:07:07,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So dedicate your tongue
to every last inch of your god.</font>

95
00:07:11,380 --> 00:07:13,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">MISS MIRA!</font>

96
00:07:14,750 --> 00:07:16,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Who are you?</font>

97
00:07:16,630 --> 00:07:17,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oop.</font>

98
00:07:20,210 --> 00:07:21,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Are you okay?</font>

99
00:07:21,170 --> 00:07:22,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I-I'm fine.</font>

100
00:07:23,330 --> 00:07:24,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But the enemy...</font>

101
00:07:26,710 --> 00:07:28,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She's a Thunder God!</font>

102
00:07:28,290 --> 00:07:29,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">On it!</font>

103
00:07:35,750 --> 00:07:38,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Where do ya think yer goin'?</font>

104
00:07:38,630 --> 00:07:41,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Do not kick...</font>

105
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">MY BEAUTIFUL BODY!</font>

106
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:47,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A heliport!</font>

107
00:07:51,380 --> 00:07:53,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Perfect for gettin' the party started!</font>

108
00:07:54,710 --> 00:07:56,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">God's Wrath!</font>

109
00:08:05,170 --> 00:08:06,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Did she just...</font>

110
00:08:07,710 --> 00:08:09,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">All Killing!</font>

111
00:08:15,420 --> 00:08:17,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Bring on the wrath!</font>

112
00:08:18,130 --> 00:08:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A cloning ability?</font>

113
00:08:19,790 --> 00:08:22,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I guess she did that
at the storehouse, too.</font>

114
00:08:22,460 --> 00:08:23,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh well.</font>

115
00:08:24,830 --> 00:08:30,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll defeat all of you
with a beautiful flick of my wrist!</font>

116
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:42,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay, so I missed one of you.</font>

117
00:08:42,330 --> 00:08:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You really think...</font>

118
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:47,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">you can beat me in midair?!</font>

119
00:08:47,420 --> 00:08:48,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Sure do.</font>

120
00:09:03,710 --> 00:09:06,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">If you're my opponent...</font>

121
00:09:06,250 --> 00:09:09,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">then this execution
just turned into a battle.</font>

122
00:09:09,330 --> 00:09:11,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What are those? Cards?!</font>

123
00:09:12,210 --> 00:09:17,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm forbidden from fighting.
"If you're forced to fight, flee instead."</font>

124
00:09:17,420 --> 00:09:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So I'll set these guys loose in the city.</font>

125
00:09:21,290 --> 00:09:22,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wha-</font>

126
00:09:22,330 --> 00:09:25,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Everyone, go!</font>

127
00:10:01,670 --> 00:10:03,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Mato Mishap in progress!</font>

128
00:10:04,540 --> 00:10:06,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Mato Mishap in progress!</font>

129
00:10:06,290 --> 00:10:07,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">An enormous Shuuki has appeared!</font>

130
00:10:07,830 --> 00:10:11,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Assess the extent of the damage
and evacuate citizens immediately!</font>

131
00:10:17,250 --> 00:10:18,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How dare you!</font>

132
00:10:19,710 --> 00:10:22,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How many can you save, I wonder?!</font>

133
00:10:22,170 --> 00:10:24,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Good luck!</font>

134
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:26,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ta-da!</font>

135
00:10:26,830 --> 00:10:30,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Kuusetsu, I'm giving you
my handmade Shuuki deck.</font>

136
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:34,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Just give the signal and
the Shuuki trapped inside pops out.</font>

137
00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:36,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I neutralized them
to put them in the cards,</font>

138
00:10:36,330 --> 00:10:39,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">but their powers will return ten seconds
after you let them out.</font>

139
00:10:39,290 --> 00:10:41,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ooh, neat!</font>

140
00:10:41,250 --> 00:10:44,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Aside from the cannon fodder,
there are four strong Shuuki in it.</font>

141
00:10:44,880 --> 00:10:48,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ordinary members of the
Demon Defense Force can't beat these guys.</font>

142
00:10:49,130 --> 00:10:52,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I brought one of 'em back to life
and upgraded it.</font>

143
00:10:52,420 --> 00:10:57,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's stronger and it spins a web
that keeps its prey alive.</font>

144
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:03,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Here's a giant Shuuki amalgamation.</font>

145
00:11:03,380 --> 00:11:05,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's a tough cookie.</font>

146
00:11:08,380 --> 00:11:10,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's everything I could ever ask for!</font>

147
00:11:10,130 --> 00:11:12,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I love you, Big Sis Shikoku!</font>

148
00:11:12,420 --> 00:11:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Call it insurance.</font>

149
00:11:21,330 --> 00:11:24,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I scattered Shuuki all over Yokohama!</font>

150
00:11:28,630 --> 00:11:32,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll show ya just how many I can save!</font>

151
00:11:32,670 --> 00:11:36,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">When creating clones,
Mira's ability allows her to choose:</font>

152
00:11:36,580 --> 00:11:38,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Clones with enhanced strength,</font>

153
00:11:39,250 --> 00:11:42,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">or she can focus on splitting into
as many clones as possible.</font>

154
00:11:44,330 --> 00:11:46,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I won't let a single person die!</font>

155
00:11:46,420 --> 00:11:47,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">All Killing!</font>

156
00:11:48,040 --> 00:11:49,420
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Scarlet Regiment</b></font>

157
00:11:48,040 --> 00:11:49,420
<font size="46"><b>{\an7}All Killing</b></font>

158
00:11:50,460 --> 00:11:51,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let's aim for numbers!</font>

159
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:53,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Push it to the limit!</font>

160
00:11:54,290 --> 00:11:56,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">HQ, please respond!</font>

161
00:11:56,130 --> 00:11:58,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A large number of Shuuki have appeared
in the Yokohama bay area!</font>

162
00:11:59,710 --> 00:12:01,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We need officers on the ground ASAP!</font>

163
00:12:04,460 --> 00:12:08,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">HQ, we're unable to contain
the gigantic Shuuki!</font>

164
00:12:08,040 --> 00:12:09,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Call the Demon Defense Force for backup!</font>

165
00:12:13,380 --> 00:12:15,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">M-Mommy...</font>

166
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:25,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This place is dangerous!
Get out of here, now!</font>

167
00:12:25,790 --> 00:12:27,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">O-okay!</font>

168
00:12:32,380 --> 00:12:34,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Follow the person in front of you
and keep moving!</font>

169
00:12:36,250 --> 00:12:37,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Help her.</font>

170
00:12:37,250 --> 00:12:38,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Of course.</font>

171
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:40,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's gonna be okay now, ma'am.</font>

172
00:12:45,210 --> 00:12:47,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's no use! We're trapped!</font>

173
00:12:47,460 --> 00:12:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">God, you're pathetic. I'll do it!</font>

174
00:13:11,250 --> 00:13:13,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">NO!</font>

175
00:13:23,250 --> 00:13:25,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's stronger than the ones
roamin' around Mato!</font>

176
00:13:26,380 --> 00:13:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Make it bow down!</font>

177
00:13:31,920 --> 00:13:33,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Kyouka!</font>

178
00:13:42,420 --> 00:13:43,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Kyouka!</font>

179
00:13:47,290 --> 00:13:48,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm all healed up.</font>

180
00:13:49,250 --> 00:13:50,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What's our game plan?</font>

181
00:13:53,040 --> 00:13:56,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We slay this thing
and regroup with the kid at the hotel.</font>

182
00:13:56,500 --> 00:13:58,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Then we meet at Rinko Park!</font>

183
00:13:58,130 --> 00:13:59,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Roger!</font>

184
00:14:10,170 --> 00:14:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Shuuki this massive in size
are extremely resilient.</font>

185
00:14:14,170 --> 00:14:16,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That just makes it a prime punching bag.</font>

186
00:14:19,790 --> 00:14:20,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Mira!</font>

187
00:14:20,630 --> 00:14:21,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yup!</font>

188
00:14:36,210 --> 00:14:38,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wow, you're really protecting them!</font>

189
00:14:43,130 --> 00:14:45,250
<font size="34" color="#ff7b55"><b>{\an7}Kinmamon</b></font>

190
00:14:43,500 --> 00:14:46,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Looked out for my crew
back in my hometown,</font>

191
00:14:46,580 --> 00:14:49,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">but I always wished I could be
in several places at once.</font>

192
00:14:50,380 --> 00:14:54,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Maybe that's why
I'm so grateful for my cloning ability.</font>

193
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:56,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And now...</font>

194
00:14:56,790 --> 00:14:58,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">See ya later!</font>

195
00:14:58,170 --> 00:15:00,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You'll feel my wrath next time we meet!</font>

196
00:15:04,170 --> 00:15:07,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A god runnin' away scared?!</font>

197
00:15:07,580 --> 00:15:10,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Talk about an ugly hag!</font>

198
00:15:07,790 --> 00:15:09,880
<font size="34" color="#dca0a0"><b>{\an7}HA!</b></font>

199
00:15:12,380 --> 00:15:15,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fine! You get to feel my wrath right now!</font>

200
00:15:16,290 --> 00:15:18,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She's going down like the rest of 'em!</font>

201
00:15:18,880 --> 00:15:21,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Used a whole buncha your energy
just now, didn'tcha?</font>

202
00:15:21,880 --> 00:15:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I bet you can can't even
clone yourself anymore.</font>

203
00:15:25,380 --> 00:15:27,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How do you expect
to fight a god like that?</font>

204
00:15:29,250 --> 00:15:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">With my skills.</font>

205
00:15:31,380 --> 00:15:33,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She doesn't learn.</font>

206
00:15:41,130 --> 00:15:42,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A feint?!</font>

207
00:15:45,630 --> 00:15:47,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Feather bullets!</font>

208
00:15:47,130 --> 00:15:49,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And she can control them remotely?!</font>

209
00:15:50,830 --> 00:15:52,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll shoot you while you're falling!</font>

210
00:15:53,670 --> 00:15:55,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Use what little ya have left!</font>

211
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:57,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">All Killing!</font>

212
00:16:03,580 --> 00:16:04,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What?!</font>

213
00:16:05,250 --> 00:16:09,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">EAT SHIT!</font>

214
00:16:14,130 --> 00:16:16,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Humans can muster up
a surprising amount of power</font>

215
00:16:16,880 --> 00:16:19,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">depending on their emotional state.</font>

216
00:16:20,250 --> 00:16:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Big Sis Shikoku was right!</font>

217
00:16:25,630 --> 00:16:28,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yer gonna learn that
wreaking havoc on Yokohama...</font>

218
00:16:29,420 --> 00:16:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">was the wrong decision!</font>

219
00:16:34,460 --> 00:16:37,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No more Miss Nice God!</font>

220
00:16:53,250 --> 00:16:54,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">With this form...</font>

221
00:16:56,330 --> 00:16:58,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">your judgment is nigh!</font>

222
00:17:01,330 --> 00:17:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A giant Shuuki is approaching the area!</font>

223
00:17:03,500 --> 00:17:05,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Please evacuate immediately!</font>

224
00:17:11,380 --> 00:17:14,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I have to catch up with
Miss Kyouka and Miss Mira, quick!</font>

225
00:17:27,040 --> 00:17:28,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Miss Kyouka!</font>

226
00:17:28,670 --> 00:17:29,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yuuki!</font>

227
00:17:32,250 --> 00:17:33,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You aren't injured, are you?</font>

228
00:17:34,170 --> 00:17:36,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can move perfectly fine now!</font>

229
00:17:36,880 --> 00:17:39,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Then we rendezvous with Mira. Let's go!</font>

230
00:17:39,420 --> 00:17:40,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yes, ma'am!</font>

231
00:17:43,290 --> 00:17:47,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She might've changed forms,
but my goal is the same!</font>

232
00:17:48,630 --> 00:17:51,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The clones she sent to counter the Shuuki
are coming back.</font>

233
00:17:52,130 --> 00:17:54,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I created these clones in numbers in mind.</font>

234
00:17:54,330 --> 00:17:58,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They won't last long, but I can
recall the ones that are close enough!</font>

235
00:18:01,130 --> 00:18:03,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now that I'm in this form...</font>

236
00:18:05,080 --> 00:18:08,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">my strength is in a class of its own!</font>

237
00:18:11,670 --> 00:18:13,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Feinting won't work a second t-</font>

238
00:18:18,540 --> 00:18:19,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She's fast!</font>

239
00:18:19,540 --> 00:18:21,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I barely have time
to activate my slime ability!</font>

240
00:18:29,670 --> 00:18:30,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Not bad.</font>

241
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:37,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Her endurance is through the roof, too!</font>

242
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:40,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That felt like the real you!</font>

243
00:18:40,500 --> 00:18:43,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I won't let your clones distract me!</font>

244
00:18:44,380 --> 00:18:45,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">God's Wrath!</font>

245
00:18:56,540 --> 00:18:58,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That was a clone, too?!</font>

246
00:18:59,750 --> 00:19:01,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She managed to make another one?!</font>

247
00:19:29,830 --> 00:19:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">If you had more clones...</font>

248
00:19:35,210 --> 00:19:38,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">you might've killed a god.</font>

249
00:19:41,330 --> 00:19:46,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But you wasted all your energy
saving bystanders instead.</font>

250
00:19:47,250 --> 00:19:49,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Mistakes come with a price!</font>

251
00:19:49,380 --> 00:19:52,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Surely you were prepared for this outcome?</font>

252
00:19:54,580 --> 00:19:57,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The god doesn't know
what she's talking about.</font>

253
00:20:01,040 --> 00:20:04,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm gonna save everyone and destroy you!</font>

254
00:20:05,210 --> 00:20:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's what I'm prepared for!</font>

255
00:20:14,250 --> 00:20:15,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Kuusetsu.</font>

256
00:20:17,080 --> 00:20:20,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">My name is Kuusetsu.
I'm one of the Eight Thunder Gods.</font>

257
00:20:21,670 --> 00:20:26,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Commander of the Demon Defense Force
2nd Squadron, Mira Kamiunten.</font>

258
00:20:31,790 --> 00:20:35,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Y'know, you're very beautiful, Mira!</font>

259
00:20:35,580 --> 00:20:39,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll show ya how the
Demon Defense Force does it, Kuusetsu!</font>

260
00:20:44,130 --> 00:20:47,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Mira's clones
have defeated all the Shuuki,</font>

261
00:20:47,130 --> 00:20:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and the city-goers are safe.</font>

262
00:20:49,080 --> 00:20:53,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Miss Mira saved me earlier,
so it's my turn to save her!</font>

263
00:21:53,460 --> 00:21:55,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Whew, I'm full!</font>

264
00:21:56,290 --> 00:21:58,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Demon Defense Force again?</font>

265
00:21:58,880 --> 00:22:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I just consumed Mira,
so I don't have room for seconds.</font>

266
00:22:12,790 --> 00:22:17,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Love beam!</font>

267
00:22:27,210 --> 00:22:30,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Wanna know and wanna do, wanna touch</font>

268
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:36,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">These feelings pouring out of me just won't stop</font>

269
00:22:36,750 --> 00:22:43,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Sweet, so sweet, let me in with your body darling</font>

270
00:22:43,380 --> 00:22:46,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">I'll domesticate you, time for a reward</font>

271
00:22:46,960 --> 00:22:51,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">With the heat from skin on skin overlapping</font>

272
00:22:51,710 --> 00:22:54,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">It's fully charged</font>

273
00:22:54,670 --> 00:22:56,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Now ready to launch!</font>

274
00:22:56,920 --> 00:23:00,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Shoot from my hand now, love love beam</font>

275
00:23:00,040 --> 00:23:03,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Aim for your heart now, love love beam</font>

276
00:23:03,750 --> 00:23:07,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Bridging the gap between us</font>

277
00:23:07,580 --> 00:23:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">And firing from point blank</font>

278
00:23:09,710 --> 00:23:11,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Yay! Yay! Yay! Yay!</font>

279
00:23:11,210 --> 00:23:14,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">You won't escape my love love beam</font>

280
00:23:14,630 --> 00:23:18,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">To the ends of the Earth, love love beam</font>

281
00:23:18,290 --> 00:23:22,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Yeah, love is what changes the world</font>

282
00:23:22,040 --> 00:23:28,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Dye it all heart-colored, even the darkness</font>

283
00:23:35,380 --> 00:23:39,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="69">Yokohama Showdown</font>

284
00:23:35,380 --> 00:23:39,040
<font size="40"><b>Episode 10</b></font>

285
00:23:35,540 --> 00:23:38,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Next time, Episode 10:
"Yokohama Showdown"!</font>

286
00:23:39,380 --> 00:23:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And this is today's bonus!</font>

287
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:42,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Allow me to explain.</font>

288
00:23:42,250 --> 00:23:45,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Kuusetsu is using her ability
that secretes a mucus to heal wounds.</font>

289
00:23:45,750 --> 00:23:47,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's all that's happening.</font>

290
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:49,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You hear me?</font>

